  "body": "### Component\n\nForge\n\n### Describe the feature you would like\n\n`git submodule` allows to specify the destination folder. It seems that `forge install` gets always the repo name (without the owner). This is sometimes too ambiguous. It would be nice to be able to specify the name of the folder that gets created under  `lib` and pass it to `git submodule add` command.\n\n### Additional context\n\n_No response_",
